Which is best for you?😱👇🏻 
1️⃣Duration ⏰ : 
🏡 At home ipl laser requires more treatment times like 8-12 times

🏥 Clinic diode laser requires less treatment times like 3-5 times 

2️⃣Budget 💴 : 
Your budget is another factor to keep in mind!
👎🏻Clinic is definitely way more costlier than at-home device! 

Final verdict? 🥇 
If you want instant and comparatively better results go for in clinic laser! ❤️

If not, home device are great for convenient use. 

✨The one I am using in the video is by “house of beauty” you can use code SUNG5 for a discount on their website #affilatecode NOT SPONSORED! ✨
